Package: swaylock
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Screen locker for Wayland compositors
 swaylock is a screen locking utility for Wayland compositors. It is
 compatible with any Wayland compositor which implements the
 ext-session-lock-v1 Wayland protocol.
 .
 Features include colour and image backgrounds, scaling modes, and PAM
 authentication support.
